Sunny salad vibes alllll Memorial day weekend LONG 😎 That means this juney ranch dressing will be on repeat… 

What you’ll need 

½ cup pure coconut cocojune

1 tsp kosher salt

½ tsp onion powder

1 tsp finely chopped garlic 

1 tbs olive oil

1 tsp dried herbs (parsley, chives, dill, thyme, rosemary, sage and oregano)

¼ tsp mustard powder

Up to 2 tbs of water

How to make 

1. Combine cocojune, salt, chopped garlic, onion powder and olive oil.

2. Now add your dried herbs of choice and that mustard powder. 

3. Finally, sprinkle in water to get your ideal dressing sitch.

4. We served ours over mixed greens, edible flowers, crunchy cucumbers and cauliflower plus some shaved carrots :)

Why I love this 3-ingredient breakfast (or dessert!) for gut health ⬇️

As a Registered Dietitian, I’m all about delicious food that does more. Cocojune is made with live and active cultures, including scientifically studied probiotic strains – BB-12, LA-5 & CRL 431 – known to support digestion, gut health, and immunity. Plus, its creamy coconut base delivers MCTs, a clean-burning fat that supports energy and satiety.

✨ Now, the recipe:
– 2 cups Pure Coconut @cocojune_organic
– ½ cup peanut or almond butter
– Top with sugar-free dark chocolate (melted), crushed peanuts & sea salt
Refrigerate for 30 minutes and enjoy all week (lasts up to 5 days)!

🌱 Dairy-free. Organic. Probiotic-packed. So simple. So functional.

Por qué me encanta este desayuno (o postre) de 3 ingredientes para la salud intestinal
Como dietista, me apasiona la comida deliciosa que también tiene una función. Cocojune está elaborado con cultivos vivos y activos, incluidos cepas probióticas científicamente estudiadas—BB-12, LA-5 y CRL 431—reconocidas por apoyar la digestión, la salud intestinal y la inmunidad. Además, su base cremosa de coco aporta MCTs, una grasa de combustión limpia que favorece la energía y la saciedad.

✨ Ahora, la receta:
– 2 tazas de cocojune
– ½ taza de mantequilla de maní o de almendras
– Encima: chocolate oscuro sin azúcar (derretido), maní triturado y sal marina
Refrigera por 30 minutos y ¡disfrútalo toda la semana! (dura hasta 5 días)

🌱 Sin lácteos. Orgánico. Rico en probióticos. Tan simple. Tan funcional.
